TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT VE.RBAT_ID CLT_HYB_ID, TC.CORP_CD CORP_OWNR_ID, 1 AS CLT_TYP_CD, VE.CLNT_NM CLT_HYB_NM, VE.RBAT_INV_EFF_DT CLT_HYB_EFF_DT, VE.RBAT_INV_TERM_DT CLT_HYB_TERM_DT, COALESCE (VE.ADDR_LN1_TXT, '') AS CLT_HYB_ADR_LN_1, COALESCE (VE.ADDR_LN2_TXT, '') AS CLT_HYB_ADR_LN_2, COALESCE (VE.CITY_NM, '') AS CLT_HYB_CITY, COALESCE (VE.ST_CD, '') AS CLT_HYB_ST, COALESCE (VE.PSTL_CD, '') AS CLT_HYB_ZIP_CD, VE.RBEL_CLNT_CD CLT_RBAT_ELG_CT_IN, VE.AP_CO_CD CLT_RBAT_CMPNY_CD, VE.BUS_SEG_CD CLT_RBAT_BUS_SG_CD, VE.CLNT_TYP_CD AS CLT_RBAT_TYP_CD FROM CLIENT_REG.V_ENRL_CLNT_DETL VE INNER JOIN VRAP.TCORP_MODEL_TYP_CD TC ON VE.MODEL_TYP_CD = TC.MODEL_TYP_CD UNION ALL SELECT DISTINCT VE.CT_ID CLT_HYB_ID, TC.CORP_CD CORP_OWNR_ID, 2 AS CLT_TYP_CD, VE.CT_NM CLT_HYB_NM, VE.CT_ID_EFF_DT CLT_HYB_EFF_DT, VE.CT_ID_TERM_DT CLT_HYB_TERM_DT, COALESCE (VE.CT_ID_ADDR_LN1_TXT, '') AS CLT_HYB_ADR_LN_1, COALESCE (VE.CT_ID_ADDR_LN2_TXT, '') AS CLT_HYB_ADR_LN_2, COALESCE (VE.CT_ID_CITY_NM, '') AS CLT_HYB_CITY, COALESCE (VE.CT_ID_ST_CD, '') AS CLT_HYB_ST, COALESCE (VE.CT_ID_PSTL_CD, '') AS CLT_HYB_ZIP_CD, MAX (VE.RBEL_CLNT_CD) CLT_RBAT_ELG_CT_IN, MAX (VE.AP_CO_CD) CLT_RBAT_CMPNY_CD, MAX (VE.BUS_SEG_CD) CLT_RBAT_BUS_SG_CD, MAX (VE.CLNT_TYP_CD) AS CLT_RBAT_TYP_CD FROM CLIENT_REG.V_ENRL_CLNT_DETL VE INNER JOIN VRAP.TCORP_MODEL_TYP_CD TC ON VE.MODEL_TYP_CD = TC.MODEL_TYP_CD WHERE CT_ID IS NOT NULL GROUP BY VE.CT_ID, TC.CORP_CD, VE.CT_NM, VE.CT_ID_EFF_DT, VE.CT_ID_TERM_DT, COALESCE (VE.CT_ID_ADDR_LN1_TXT, ''), COALESCE (VE.CT_ID_ADDR_LN2_TXT, ''), COALESCE (VE.CT_ID_CITY_NM, ''), COALESCE (VE.CT_ID_ST_CD, ''), COALESCE (VE.CT_ID_PSTL_CD, '') UNION ALL SELECT 0 CLT_HYB_ID, 1 CORP_OWNR_ID, 2 AS CLT_TYP_CD, '<NOT AVAILABLE PRE 2013>' CLT_HYB_NM, '1/1/1111' CLT_HYB_EFF_DT, '12/31/9999' CLT_HYB_TERM_DT, '' CLT_HYB_ADR_LN_1, '' CLT_HYB_ADR_LN_2, '' CLT_HYB_CITY, '' CLT_HYB_ST, '' CLT_HYB_ZIP_CD, 1 CLT_RBAT_ELG_CT_IN, '-1' CLT_RBAT_CMPNY_CD, '0' CLT_RBAT_BUS_SG_CD, '0' CLT_RBAT_TYP_CD FROM SYSIBM.SYSDUMMY1 WITH UR

), 1, 0 )
